WEBVTT

00:00.055 --> 00:01.773
Previously on "The Arrangement"...

00:01.798 --> 00:03.734
- Megan Morrison.
- You're an actress, right?

00:03.768 --> 00:05.046
I am in fact an actress.

00:05.071 --> 00:07.015
Or are you just a waitress
who's trying to act?

00:07.040 --> 00:09.476
- Nic? What's going on?
- Nothing's going on.

00:09.501 --> 00:12.343
- Who are you?
- I'm Annika, and I'm pregnant.

00:12.391 --> 00:13.998
You slept with her? Oh, my God.

00:14.023 --> 00:15.031
What are you doing? Megan?

00:15.056 --> 00:16.429
You better start doing
whatever actor-y shit

00:16.461 --> 00:17.696
it is you need to do to get ready,

00:17.729 --> 00:18.964
because you've only got two hours.

00:18.998 --> 00:20.075
Until what?

00:20.100 --> 00:22.469
Until you read with Kyle West.

00:22.510 --> 00:24.645
The whole world wants
to work with Kyle West.

00:24.670 --> 00:26.325
He could do whatever he wants.

00:26.350 --> 00:27.684
I'm going to Oslo.

00:27.806 --> 00:28.999
It's the only way to stop this.

00:29.161 --> 00:31.453
What makes you think
that you can stop it?

00:31.677 --> 00:32.979
Megan, wait.

00:33.012 --> 00:34.351
That was what acting is supposed to be.

00:34.376 --> 00:36.379
Can I take you to lunch?

00:37.712 --> 00:38.717
Kyle's not in a good place.

00:38.751 --> 00:40.586
Is there any way of getting
Lisbeth's itinerary for Venice?

00:40.619 --> 00:41.703
There's always a way.

00:41.728 --> 00:44.235
I never thought Lisbeth would
just bail on me at our wedding.

00:44.290 --> 00:45.525
Did she ever explain herself?

00:45.558 --> 00:47.527
Something about getting
lost in my world.

00:47.561 --> 00:49.363
Took that nobody actress to Mexico.

00:49.396 --> 00:51.009
I don't want to clean
up another train wreck.

00:51.034 --> 00:53.368
Well, then let's makes sure
this one stays on the rails.

00:53.393 --> 00:56.118
- This is an offer from Kyle West.
- For the movie?

00:56.143 --> 00:58.639
He's offering you a contract marriage.

00:58.671 --> 01:00.373
We just met.

01:00.406 --> 01:02.086
I think that you are amazing.

01:02.111 --> 01:03.643
Come to Venice with me.

01:03.676 --> 01:05.513
To Italy?

01:06.290 --> 01:08.025
You're off to a great start.

01:08.050 --> 01:10.254
- But you have to keep doing it.
- I plan to.

01:10.279 --> 01:12.047
Okay, Annika, let's see what we can do

01:12.072 --> 01:13.724
about getting you an agent.

01:19.398 --> 01:21.998
Imagine a table in front of you.

01:22.733 --> 01:25.170
Now take the last 48 hours of your life

01:25.211 --> 01:27.445
and lay it on that table.

01:27.913 --> 01:31.250
Spread it out, and take
a good look at your work.

01:31.610 --> 01:33.461
It's extraordinary, isn't it?

01:34.251 --> 01:37.109
Each you came here feeling lost

01:37.626 --> 01:40.038
and trapped by a narrative
written by others.

01:40.905 --> 01:42.491
And in four days...

01:43.428 --> 01:45.101
just four days...

01:46.218 --> 01:47.853
you found the vision
to design the blueprint

01:47.885 --> 01:49.754
for your better self.

01:54.487 --> 01:56.919
And this is just the beginning.

01:57.687 --> 02:01.167
From now on, when you look at your life

02:01.200 --> 02:03.051
and the people in it,

02:03.808 --> 02:05.665
things will look different.

02:06.938 --> 02:09.743
Non-productives will
fade to the background,

02:09.973 --> 02:12.641
while possibility comes into focus.

02:13.222 --> 02:14.985
But be prepared

02:15.415 --> 02:17.885
as you begin to build your new life,

02:18.152 --> 02:21.871
people from your old life
may disagree with your design.

02:22.355 --> 02:24.215
Just keep building

02:24.683 --> 02:27.879
and know that IHM is
always here for you.

02:29.597 --> 02:32.589
You're looking through the
right end of the telescope now.

02:37.671 --> 02:39.607
You want to get a quick
workout in before breakfast?

02:39.639 --> 02:41.408
I just showered.

02:43.130 --> 02:44.632
But maybe

02:44.657 --> 02:47.943
you had a different
kind of workout in mind.

02:48.928 --> 02:50.701
Say hi to Ben.

02:53.817 --> 02:55.686
Hi, Ben.

02:55.711 --> 02:57.387
I'm Megan.

02:57.412 --> 02:59.458
Hi. Nice to meet you.

03:00.528 --> 03:01.911
Yeah.

03:01.936 --> 03:03.805
I thought I could play
this cool, but this...

03:03.830 --> 03:06.656
this is really awkward, isn't it?

03:06.681 --> 03:09.200
Um, not at all.

03:09.757 --> 03:11.301
That's not true. Okay.

03:11.325 --> 03:13.934
I'm gonna just get my towel now.

