- Cheers.
- Whoo.

34:23.016 --> 34:25.493
Ohh, sporto,

34:25.518 --> 34:27.085
you mind if I get the next one?

34:27.110 --> 34:28.612
It's all you, man.

34:28.638 --> 34:31.039
- You're out of here?
- I got to get going. Yeah, yeah.

34:31.525 --> 34:33.172
Ohh.

34:34.795 --> 34:37.539
I never got to hear your story.

34:38.524 --> 34:40.594
I'm just another
actress hoping for a part

34:40.619 --> 34:42.755
in the next Daisy Parsons movie.

35:18.739 --> 35:20.074
Hey.

35:20.099 --> 35:21.601
Hey, you, beautiful.

35:21.626 --> 35:23.099
Hey.

35:23.124 --> 35:24.292
Hey.

35:24.794 --> 35:27.450
Hey. Why are you leaving?

35:27.475 --> 35:29.444
I'm going back to my hotel.

35:29.469 --> 35:31.505
Wow, you speak very good Italian.

35:31.530 --> 35:34.247
Look, I'd rather walk by myself, okay?

35:34.272 --> 35:35.456
I wanna be alone.

35:35.481 --> 35:37.651
Oh, no, no, you are not serious.

35:37.708 --> 35:39.543
American girls like to have fun.

35:39.568 --> 35:40.825
Do not touch me!

35:41.982 --> 35:43.856
Ow, get your hands off of me!

35:43.881 --> 35:45.325
Hey!

35:45.521 --> 35:46.786
Come here.

35:47.509 --> 35:49.200
- You okay?
- Yeah.

35:49.616 --> 35:52.747
Wait, Kyle, just let him go.

35:54.653 --> 35:56.464
Kyle.

36:00.056 --> 36:01.691
What did he do to you?

36:01.716 --> 36:02.785
I'm okay.

36:02.810 --> 36:04.099
No, he was all over you, Megan.

36:04.124 --> 36:05.621
- You can't just say that you're okay.
- I am.

36:05.646 --> 36:07.949
I don't know how it
looked, but I'm fine.

36:09.177 --> 36:11.313
What the hell were you thinking
leaving the hotel like that?

36:11.345 --> 36:12.847
I was on my way to the gym,

36:12.880 --> 36:14.972
and I ran into some friends,
and they invited me out.

36:14.997 --> 36:16.924
It is not that simple, okay?

36:16.949 --> 36:18.042
You have to think.

36:18.067 --> 36:19.464
You can't just do
whatever the hell you want.

36:19.489 --> 36:21.175
And you can't act like this is my fault,

36:21.200 --> 36:23.113
because it's not.

36:23.824 --> 36:25.347
Please, look. Look,
please. Look, please.

36:25.372 --> 36:27.308
Not now, okay?

36:27.862 --> 36:29.764
Look, I said not now.

36:30.025 --> 36:32.230
God damn it. I told you to stop!

36:32.610 --> 36:34.058
Oh, my God.

36:40.186 --> 36:41.721
Shit.

36:52.175 --> 36:53.777
I need you.

37:17.867 --> 37:20.003
It's taken care of.

37:48.932 --> 37:50.577
That guy,

37:50.733 --> 37:53.444
he jumped out at the wrong time,

37:53.469 --> 37:55.256
and you reacted.

37:57.972 --> 37:59.890
You're a human being.

38:02.211 --> 38:03.866
It's gonna be okay.

38:04.497 --> 38:05.897
I promise.

38:26.913 --> 38:28.297
Ohh.

39:05.474 --> 39:08.201
Hey, you sure you want to
stick around for all this?

39:08.226 --> 39:10.195
It's gonna get old real quick.

39:10.220 --> 39:12.355
I'm not leaving your side.

39:20.531 --> 39:22.334
Terence?

39:23.545 --> 39:25.514
You didn't have to come
all the way out here.

39:25.547 --> 39:26.983
But I'm glad you did.

39:28.616 --> 39:30.281
It's all good, man.

39:34.190 --> 39:36.085
Hello, darling.

39:36.491 --> 39:38.640
This is a little extreme, isn't it?

39:39.762 --> 39:41.539
I don't think so.

39:42.039 --> 39:44.125
So after one situation...
that I handled...

39:44.150 --> 39:46.918
you've decided that
shadowing Kyle is a good idea?

39:46.951 --> 39:48.477
That's not why I'm here.

39:57.351 --> 39:59.154
So was it seeing Kyle with Lisbeth?

39:59.204 --> 40:01.609
Is that what bothered you so much?

40:02.103 --> 40:03.507
Excuse me?

40:03.532 --> 40:05.201
I'm just trying to understand
why you left the hotel

40:05.226 --> 40:07.528
last night without telling anybody.

40:07.717 --> 40:08.751
How...

40:08.776 --> 40:10.687
Just answer the question.

40:14.030 --> 40:16.370
Kyle fell asleep, and I...

40:16.536 --> 40:19.394
ran into some friends,
and I sent him a text.

40:19.687 --> 40:21.370
DeAnn didn't tell you?

40:21.878 --> 40:23.365
You made a commitment to be mindful

40:23.390 --> 40:24.792
of how your actions affect Kyle.

40:24.817 --> 40:26.485
Do you think you honored that?

40:26.808 --> 40:28.706
Kyle and I already dealt with this.

40:28.761 --> 40:31.079
It's over, and we're good, so...

40:31.722 --> 40:35.230
I don't really understand why
you're getting in my face right now.

40:52.656 --> 40:54.867
Does this look familiar?

40:59.943 --> 41:02.578
So either you can't keep a commitment,

41:02.753 --> 41:04.822
or you're just not that bright.

41:06.524 --> 41:09.194
More like you have no clue about me.

41:09.884 --> 41:11.648
You signed a contract

41:11.673 --> 41:14.242
that you've given me grounds
to terminate right now.

41:14.267 --> 41:16.289
Maybe that's what you want.

41:17.988 --> 41:20.524
No, that's not what I want.

41:21.141 --> 41:23.413
That's not what Kyle wants either.

41:24.169 --> 41:27.445
But you better manage your
problem with authority,

41:28.555 --> 41:30.823
or this whole this will be over.

41:35.688 --> 41:37.462
Okay, everybody ready.

41:37.487 --> 41:39.033
We have speed?

41:39.470 --> 41:41.806
Speed. Kyle West, take one.

41:42.439 --> 41:43.650
Action.

